Texts.Eng: I wasn't sure if you'd beat that one, but I guess I was wrong to doubt you! You've earned yourself access to a few more powerful weapon attachments!

I've got some more weapon attachments in store for you, if you can beat my next challenge. I want you to ^green;find and kill ^orange;5 Sandspitters^reset;, but it won't be easy! ^green;You can find the large worm-like beasts on desert worlds ^reset;- watch out for the sand they spit at you!
